snippet.title: Vangaro Tactics | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2221530/Vangaro_Tactics/

Command colorful troops into tactical turn-based battles in Vangaro Tactics! Infiltrate enemy outposts on the Stealth Missions: mine, recruit, move wisely, and you'll stand a chance. Know your commanders and exclusive units to make the most of each faction.

Vangaro Tactics is an upcoming turn-based strategy game made by solo developer niadocraz.
Trailer music by @SergisPiano


#turnbased #gametrailer #indiegame
